findings.title: Presence of Unused Variables
findings.description: Unused variables are allowed in Solidity and they do not pose a direct security issue. It is best practice though to avoid them as they can save gas consumption and increase the cleanliness and readability of the whole code base.

findings.title: Owner can set total taxes up to 100%
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the ability to set total taxes up to 100%, which could potentially lead to unintended consequences.
